OL,4,G2150FDire Straits: On The Night 1992
OL,5,     GMark Knopfler and the band
OL,6,     Gperform songs from their final
OL,7,     Galbum On Every Street alongside
OL,8,     Gtheir greatest hits. Concert film
OL,9,     Gcapturing Dire Straits during
OL,10,     Gtheir last world tour in 1992.
